    {
      "chinese": "會移地、移住的最根本原因，有以下幾個主要的情況：為了擴大部落版圖；遠離外族侵犯；為了獵場；因為迷信；為了水源；有時因瘟疫；有時是天災造成土地的破損、流失；也有被統治者強行遷村，尤其是日本時代與民國時代。",
      "ab": "Kudra ngualaylringa lini si apataluelaela, amani kikay tapiane kay makucingalre ku takipadradresengane lini, amani ki asuivane ku taikayyane tucekele, amani ku akidailane ki badha, amani ki taalupane, amani ki lrisi, amani ki taaciladhane, yakay lungualay ki sualrubu, laikay lungualay ki tangilisiane ki takiumukane si ngilisianenga ku kadaengane, yakay lukakiapataluela ki wakadrenge liniane ka sihu, kay sakanadripungu si kelanga kay Lawtia.",
